title: I See Stars - Renegades Forever [2013]
description:
I See Stars is an American electronicore rock band that formed in 2006 from Warren, Michigan. They are considered one the foremost pioneers of the emerging subgenre electronicore. Their debut album, 3-D, featured a guest appearance from Bizzy Bone of Bone Thugs-n-Harmony. The album peaked at No. 176 on the Billboard 200.
